{"tid":997539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【1月27日】鳥羽、伏見之戰","createTime":"2019-01-27T08:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T10:54:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd3bc6d5a81622e9335e809c02c8ad2accdb3c6d","tid":997539,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"1868年1月27日，支持日本明治天皇的新政府軍，與支持德川家的舊幕府軍，在京都南郊的鳥羽、伏見一帶交戰，日本近代最重要的內戰「戊辰戰爭」正式爆發。<br />\n<br />\n在維新派的壓力下，德川幕府1867年被迫「大政奉還」，不過仍企圖建立以德川家為首的新政府；維新派則堅持德川家離開政治中心，除要求其「辭官納地」，更於江戶（現東京都）四處放火挑釁。德川派忍無可忍，派出1.5萬舊幕府軍進軍京都，試圖掌控局勢。<br />\n<br />\n舊幕府軍與5000新政府軍於鳥羽、伏見一帶交戰，剛開始還佔據優勢，不過新政府軍的火砲數量遠高於舊幕府軍，加上天皇稍後正式宣布後者為「叛軍」，讓舊幕府軍全面潰敗，總大將德川慶喜更拋下軍隊，自海路撤回江戶。鳥羽、伏見之戰後，舊幕府軍各自為政，遭新政府軍各個擊破，最後開啟日本現代化的「明治維新」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/1月27日軍史上的今天-鳥羽-伏見之戰-160000512.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F1%E6%9C%8827%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E9%B3%A5%E7%BE%BD-%E4%BC%8F%E8%A6%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-160000512.html&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=fee9291a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/1月27日軍史上的今天-鳥羽-伏見之戰-160000512.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.wenzhangba.com/allimg/180510/1P510203002-2c8-0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.wenzhangba.com%2Fallimg%2F180510%2F1P510203002-2c8-0.png&h=59c99f88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68895db4d33ec14bca532a5ad11dcdf71383d127","tid":997539,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"追憶 人誅篇<br />\n拍真人未"},{"pid":"f06dc65ed7145cc9c2c6f4e2b4326aa529eabb47","tid":997539,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273600068ea392805f25992d1a985a7cde1751cd","tid":997539,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}